-- Chalco to Reduce Alumina Spot Prices by 7% to 2,650 Yuan Per Metric Ton
-- Bloomberg News
-- 2010-07-01T03:41:39Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2010-07-01/chalco-to-reduce-alumina-spot-prices-by-7-to-2-650-yuan-per-metric-ton.html

          
          
             Aluminum Corp. of China Ltd., known
as Chalco, cut the spot price for alumina by 7 percent to 2,650
yuan ($391) a metric ton, the Beijing-based company said today
on its Web site.  
